knowledgeGraph.title: Logan Health Medical Center
knowledgeGraph.description: Logan Health Medical Center is a 622-bed non-profit, tertiary, research and academic medical center located in Kalispell, Montana, servicing the northern Montana region. Formerly Kalispell Regional Medical Center, the hospital is owned by Logan Health and is the flagship hospital of the system.
